it's Ling Xiao,

67
00:05:03,510 --> 00:05:04,720
for hurting you to this extent.

68
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,000
Wan'er,

69
00:05:07,750 --> 00:05:08,870
I'm your best friend

70
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,680
and your closest brother.

71
00:05:44,420 --> 00:05:50,020
♪Flowers fall in the courtyard,
