72
00:05:52,060 --> 00:05:58,340
♪Playing the Guqin under the moon,
recalling his poem♪

73
00:06:04,510 --> 00:06:05,870
You and the child can't withstand

74
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,920
a life of wandering anymore.

75
00:06:08,630 --> 00:06:09,950
Consider Baiyu City

76
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,870
as your home from now on.

77
00:06:13,860 --> 00:06:17,060
♪Years have passed, the flowers
have bloomed again♪

78
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:21,020
♪In this life without you,
day and night feel endless♪

79
00:06:21,300 --> 00:06:24,460
♪In this old dreamland,
memories of past lives are locked away♪

80
00:06:24,620 --> 00:06:27,780
♪I didn't see you when I woke up
and opened the windows♪

81
00:06:27,980 --> 00:06:31,180
