♪The letter from afar has yet to arrive♪

85
00:06:42,700 --> 00:06:46,140
♪If we hadn't known
and understood each other♪

86
00:06:46,340 --> 00:06:50,380
♪We wouldn't have been bothered by love♪

87
00:06:50,700 --> 00:06:57,340
♪All the sorrowful expressions
will be gone when your return♪

88
